HEADWORD: Aversely
<hw>A*verse"ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Backward; in a
backward direction; <as>as, emitted <ex>aversely</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>With repugnance or aversion; unwillingly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Averseness</ent>⟦br⟧
